hadiths[29]{hadithnumber,text}:
1464,"Mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! hum log shikari hain? ( shikar key ehkam bataiye?) aap ney farmaya : '' jab tum ( shikar key liye ( apna kutta chhodo aur is par Allah ka naam yani Bismillah padh lo phir wo tumharey liye shikar ko roke rakhey to usey khaao ? mainey kaha : agar-che wo shikar ko maar daley , aap ney farmaya : '' agar-che maar daley , mainey arz kiya : hum log teer andaz hain ( to iskey barey mein farmaiye ? (aap ney farmaya : ''tumhara teer jo shikar karey usey khaao.''  mainey arz kiya : hum safar karney waley log hain, Yahud aur Nasara aur Majoos ki bastiyon sey guzartey hain aur unkey bartanon key ilawa hamarey paas koi bartan nahin hota (to kya hum unkey bartanon mein kha lein?) aap ney farmaya : ''agar tum uskey ilawa koi bartan na paa sako to usey pani sey dho lo phir is mein khaao piyo.''  is baab mein Adi bin Hatim sey bhi riwayat hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Abu-Solba Khushni ka naam Jursum hai, unhen Jursum bin Naashib aur Jursum bin Qais bhi kaha jata hai."
1465,"Mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! hum log apney sadhaaey padhi. huye kuttey ( shikar key liye ( rawana kartey hain ( ye kya hai?) aap ney farmaya : ''wo jo kuchh tumharey liye roke rakhen usey khaao.''  mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! agar-che wo shikar ko maar dalen ? aap ney farmaya : '' agar-che wo ( shikar ko) maar dalen ( phir bhi halal hai) jab tak unkey sath doosra kutta shareek na ho.''  Adi bin Hatim kehtey hain : mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! hum log (mea'raaz) (hathiyar ki chaudaan) sey shikar kartey hain, (us ka kya hukm hai?) aap ney farmaya : '' jo (hathiyar ki nauk sey) phat jaey usey khaao aur jo uskey arz (baghair dhaardar hissey yani chaudaan) sey mar jaey usey mat khaao. is sanad sey bhi isi jaisi hadees riwayat ki gaee hai, magar is mein hai «وسئل an المعراض» ''yani aap sey mea'raaz key barey mein puchha gaya.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1466,"Hamein majusiyon key kuttey key shikar sey mana kiya gaya hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. 2- aksar ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, ye log majusi key kuttey key shikar ki ijazat nahin detey."
1467,"Mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey baaz key shikar key mutalliq puchha ? to aap ney farmaya : '' wo tumharey liye jo roke rakhey usey khaao.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- hum is hadees ko sirf isi sanad (an Majaalid an Sha'abi) sey jantey hain. 2- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, ye log baaz aur shikre key shikar mein muzaaeqa (harj) nahin samajhtey. 3- Mujahid kehtey hain : baaz wo perinda hai jis sey shikar kiya jata hai, ye us (Jawareh) mein dakhil hai jis ka zikr Allah Taala ney aayate-karima : (وما علمتم من الجوارح ) mein kiya hai unhoney (jawareh) ki tafseer kuttey aur us parindey sey ki hai jin sey shikar kiya jata hai. 4- baaz ehle-ilm ney baaz key shikar ki rukhsat di hai agar-che wo shikar mein sey kuchh kha ley , ye log kehtey hain ke uski taalim ka matlab hai ke jab usey shikar key liye chhoda jaey to wo hukm qubul karey, jabke baaz logon ney isey makrooh kaha hai, lekin aksar fuqaha kehtey hain : baaz ka shikar khaya jaeyga chahey wo shikar ka kuchh hissa kha ley."
1468,"Mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! main shikar ko teer maarta hun phir agley din is mein apna teer paata hun (us shikar ka kya hukm hai? (aap ney farmaya : '' jab tumhen malum ho jaey ke tumharey hi teer ney shikar ko maara hai aur tum is mein kisi aur darindey ka asar na dekho to usey khaao.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Shoba ney ye hadees abu-Bashar sey aur abdul-Malik bin Maisraa ney Saeed bin Juber sey , unhoney Adi bin Hatim sey riwayat ki hai, dono riwaayatein sahih hain. 3- is bab mein Abu-Solba Khushni sey bhi riwayat hai, 4- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai."
1469,"Mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey shikar key mutalliq puchha to aap ney farmaya : '' tum apna teer phainktey waqt is par Allah ka naam (yani Bismillah) padho , phir agar usey mara huwa paao to bhi kha lo , siwaye iskey ke usey pani mein gira huwa paao to na khaao isliye ke tumhen nahin malum ke pani ney isey maara hai ya tumharey teer ney.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1470,"Mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey sadhaaey huye kuttey key mutalliq puchha to aap ney farmaya : '' jab tum apna sadhaayaa huwa kutta rawana karo, aur) bhejtey waqt us par) Allah ka naam (yani Bismillah) padh lo to tumharey liye jo kuchh wo roke rakhey usey khaao aur agar wo shikar sey kuchh kha ley to mat khaao, isliye ke usney shikar apney liye roka hai.'' , mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! aap ka kya khayal hai agar hamarey kuttey key sath doosrey kuttey shareek ho jaeyn? aap ney farmaya : ''tum ney Allah ka naam ( yani Bismillah) apney hi kuttey par padha hai doosrey kuttey par nahin.'' Sufiyan ( Sory ( kehtey hain : aap ney uskey liye uska khana durust nahin samjha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- zabiha aur shikar key silsiley mein Sahaba kiram mein sey baaz ehle-ilm aur doosrey logon key nazdik isi par amal hai ke jab wo pani mein gir jaeyn to unhen koi na khaye aur baaz log zabiha key barey mein kehtey hain : jab uska gala kaat diya jaey, phir pani mein girey aur mar jaey to usey khaya jaeyga, Abdullah bin Mubarak ka yehi qol hai. 2- ehle-ilm ka is masle mein ke jab kutta shikar ka kuchh hissea kha ley ikhtilaf hai, aksar ehle-ilm kehtey hain : jab kutta shikar sey kha ley to usey mat khao , Sufiyan Sory , Abdullah bin Mubarak , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka yehi qol hai. 3- jabke Sahaba kiram mein sey baaz ehle-ilm aur doosrey logon ney khaney ki rukhsat di hai, agar-che is mein sey kuttey ney kha liya ho."
1471,Mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey baghair par key teer key shikar key mutalliq puchha to aap ney farmaya : '' jisey tum ney dhaar sey maara hai usey khaao aur jisey arz ( baghair dhaardar hissey yani chodaan) sey maara hai to wo « وقيذ » hai (yani wo shikar jise laathi dande se peetkar maara ho). is sanad sey bhi isi jaisi hadees marvi (riwayat) hui hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees sahih hai. 2- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai.
1472,"Unki qom key eik aadmi ney eik ya do khargosh ka shikar kiya aur unko patthar sey zibeh kiya, phir in ko latkaaey rakha yahan tak ke usney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey mulaqat ki aur iskey barey mein puchha , to aap ney isey khaney ka hukm diya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees ki riwayat mein Shaabi key shagirdon ka ikhtilaf hai, Dawud bin Ubai Hind baasand Shaabi an Muhammad bin Safwan (Raziallahu anhu) riwayat kartey hain, aur Aasim Al-Ahwal baasand Shaabi an Safwan bin Muhammad ya Muhammad bin Safwan riwayat kartey hain, (Safwaan bin Muhammad key bajaey Muhammad bin Safwan ziyada sahih hai) Jabir Jaafi bhi basanad (Shaabi an Jabir bin Abdullah) Qatada ki hadees ki tarah riwayat kartey hain, is baat ka ehtimaal hai ke Shaabi ki riwayat dono sey ho. 2- Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain : Jabir ki Shaabi sey riwayat ghair mehfooz hai. 3- is bab mein Muhammad bin Safwan , Raafey aur Adi bin Hatim sey bhi ahadees aai hain. 4- baaz ehle-ilm ney patthar sey zibeh karney ki rukhsat (chhoot) di hai. 5- ye log khargosh khaney mein koi harj nahin samajhtey, aksar ehle-ilm ka yehi qol hai. 6- baaz log khargosh khaney ko makrooh samajhtey hain."
1473,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney « مجثمة » key khaney sey mana farmaya (مجثمة). us janwer ya perinde ko kehtey hain, jisey baandh kar teer sey maara jaey yahan tak ke wo mar jaey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Darda ki hadees gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Arbaz bin Saariya , Anas , ibne-Umar , ibne-Abbas , Jabir aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1474,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Fateh khaibar key din har kuchli waley darindey panjey waley perindey padhi. , paaltu gadhey key gosht , « مجثمة » aur « خليسة » sey mana farmaya , aap ney hamila (laundi jo naee naee musalmanon ki qaid mein aaye) key sath jab tak wo bacha na janey jima (sambhog) karney sey bhi mana farmaya. Raavi Muhammad bin Yahya Qatai kehtey hain : abu-Aasim sey « مجثمة » key barey mein puchha gaya to unhoney kaha : perindey ya kisi doosrey janwer ko baandh kar is par teer andazi ki jaey ( yahan tak ke wo mar jaey (aur un sey « خليسة » (khaleesa) key barey mein puchha gaya to unhoney kaha : « خليسة » wo janwer hai, jis ko bhediya ya darinda pakdey aur us sey koi aadmi usey chheen ley phir wo janwer zibeh kiye janey sey pehley uskey haath mein mar jaey."
1475,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney kisi jandaar ko nishana bananey sey mana farmaya hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai.
1476,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''janeen (jo bachcha pet me ho)  ki maa ka zibeh hi janeen (jo bachcha pet me ho) key zibeh key liye kafi hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- aur ye is sanad key ilawa sey bhi abu Saeed Khudri sey hai. 3- is bab mein Jabir , abu-Umama , Abu-Darda , aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain. 4- Sahaba kiram aur in key ilawa logon mein sey ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, aur yehi Sufiyan Sory , ibne-Mubarak , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai."
1477,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney har kuchli daant waley darindey sey mana farmaya. is sanad sey bhi isi jaisi hadees marvi (riwayat hui) hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
1478,"Fatah khaibar key din Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney paaltu gadhey , khachchar key gosht , har kuchli daant waley darindey aur panjey waley parindey ko haram kar diya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Jabir ki hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera , Arbaz bin Saariya aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1479,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney har kuchli daant waley darindey ko haram qarar diya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- Sahaba kiram aur deegar logon mein sey aksar ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, Abdullah bin Mubarak , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi yehi qol hai padhi. ."
1480,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Madina tashrif laye, wahan key log ( zinda ( oonton key kohaan aur) zinda ( bakriyon ki putth kaat'tey they, aap ney farmaya : '' zinda janwer ka kaataa huwa gosht murdar hai.'' is sanad sey bhi usi jaisi hadees marvi (riwayat hui) hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum is hadees ko sirf Zaid bin Aslam ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 2- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai."
1481,"Mainey puchha : Allah key Rasool ! kya zibeh (sharaee) sirf halaq aur labba hi mein hoga? aap ney farmaya : ''agar uski raan mein bhi teer maar do to kafi hoga.''  Yazeed bin Harun kehtey hain : ye hukm zarurat key sath khas hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf Hammad bin Salma hi ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 2- is hadees key ilawa abu Ushra ki koi aur hadees in key baap sey hum nahin jantey hain, abu Ushra key naam key silsiley mein ikhtilaf hai : baaz log kehtey hain : unka naam Usama bin Qihtim hai, aur kaha jata hai unka naam Yasar bin Barz hai aur ibne Balz bhi kaha jata hai, ye bhi kaha jata hai ke unka naam Utaarid hai daada ki taraf un ki nisbat ki gaee hai. 3- is bab mein Raafey bin khadij sey bhi riwayat aai hai."
1482,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo chhipkali ko pehli chot mein maareyga us ko itna sawab hoga, agar us ko dusri chot mein maareyga to us ko itna sawab hoga aur agar us ko teesri chot mein maareyga to us ko itna sawab hoga.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Masood , Saad , Aaisha aur Umme Shareek sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1483,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''saanpon ko maaro , khas taur sey us sanp ko maaro jiski peeth pe do ( kaali ( lakeerein hoti hain aur us sanp ko jiski dam chhoti hoti hai isliye ke ye dono beenai (aankho ki roshni) ko zaayel (khatm) kar detey hain aur hamal ko gira detey hain.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey marvi hai wo abu-Lubaba (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney iskey baad gharon mein rehney waley saanpon ko jinhen « عوامر » ( bastiyon mein rehney waley saanp) kaha jata hai, maarney sey mana farmaya padhi. : ibne-Umar is hadees ko Zaid bin Khattab padhi. sey bhi riwayat kartey hain. 3- is bab mein ibne-Masood , Aaisha , Abu-Hurera aur Sehal bin Saad (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain. 4- Abdullah bin Mubarak kehtey hain : saanpon key qiamon mein sey us sanp ko bhi maarna makrooh hai jo patla (aur safed) hota hai goya ke wo chaandi ho, wo chalney mein bal nahin khata balke sidha chalta hai."
1484,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tumharey gharon mein gharelu sanp rehtey hain, tum unhen teen baar aagah kar do tum tangi mein ho (yani dekho dobara nazar na aana warna tangi aur pareshani sey dochaar hoga) phir agar us tanbih key baad koi sanp nazar aaye to usey maar dalo.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is hadees ko Ubedullah bin umr ney basanad :(صيفِ an أبي سعيد الْدري) riwayat kiya hai. jab ke Malik bin Anas ney is hadees ko basanad :(صيفِ an أبي السائب مول هشام بن زهرة an أبي سعيد an النبِ صلى الله عليه وسلم) riwayat kiya, is hadees main eik qissa bhi mazkur hai. hum sey is hadees ko Ansari ney basanad (معن an مالک an صيف an أبی السائب an أبی سعيدالْدری) sey riwayat kiya hai, aur ye Ubedullah bin umr ki riwayat sey ziyada sahih hai, Muhammad bin Ajlan ney bhi Saifi sey Malik ki tarah riwayat ki hai."
1485,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab ghar mein sanp nikley to us sey kaho : hum Nuh aur Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Dawud key ehad aur iqrar ki taraf sey ye chahtey hain ke tum hamen na sataoo phir agar wo dobara nikley to usey maar do.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum is hadees ko Sabit Bunani ki riwayat sey sirf ibne-Abi Leila hi key tareeq sey jantey hain."
1486,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' agar ye baat na hoti ke kuttey deegar makhluqat ki tarah eik makhluq hain to main tamam kutton ko maar dalney ka hukm deta , so ab tum un mein sey har kaley siyah kuttey ko maar dalo.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abdullah bin Mughaffal ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar , Jabir , abu-Raafey , aur abu-Ayyub (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain. 3- baaz hadeeson mein marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke kaala kutta shetan hota hai. 4- « الأسود البهيم » us kuttey ko kehtey hain jis mein safedi bilkul na ho. 5- baaz ehle-ilm ney kaaley kuttey key kiye shikar ko makrooh samjha hai."
1487,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney aisa kutta paala ya rakha jo sadhaayaa huwa shikari aur janweron ki nigrani karney wala na ho to uskey sawab mein sey har din do qeeraat key barabar kam hoga.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke aap ney ye bhi farmaya : (أو كلب زرع) ''ya wo kutta kheti ki nigrani karney wala na ho.'' 3- is bab mein Abdullah bin Mughaffal, Abu-Hurera , aur Sufiyan bin Ubai Zuhair (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1488,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney shikari ya janweron ki nigrani karney waley kuttey key ilawa deegar kutton ko maar dalney ka hukm diya ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey kaha gaya : Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ye bhi kehtey they : (أو كلب زرع) ya kheti ki nigrani karney waley kuttey (yani ye bhi mustashnaa (apwaad) hain), to ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ney kaha : Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) key paas kheti thi (isliye unhoney iskey barey mein puchha hoga). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1489,"Main un logon mein sey hon jo Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key Mubarak chehrey sey darkht ki shaakhon ko hata rahey they aur aap khutba dey rahey they, aap ney farmaya : '' agar ye baat na hoti ke kuttey deegar makhluqat ki tarah eik makhluq hain to main inhen maarney ka hukm deta padhi. , so ab tum in mein sey har siyah kaaley kuttey ko maar dalo, jo ghar waley bhi shikari , ya kheti ki nigrani karney waley ya bakriyon ki nigrani karney waley kutton key siwa koi doosra kutta baandhey rakhtey hain har din unkey amal (sawab) sey eik qeeraat kam hoga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- ye hadees basanad :(حسن البصریٰ an عبد الله بن مغفل an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) marvi (riwayat hui) hai."
1490,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo shakhs bhi janweron ki nigrani karney waley ya shikari ya kheti ki nigrani karney waley kuttey key siwa koi doosra kutta paaleyga to har roz uskey sawab mein sey eik qeeraat kam hoga.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Ata bin abi Ribah ney kutta paalney ki rukhsat di hai agar-che kisi key paas eik hi bakri kyon na ho. is sanad sey bhi Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey isi jaisi hadees marvi (riwayat hui) hai.
1491,"Mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! kal hum dushman sey milengey aur hamarey paas (janwer zibeh karney key liye) chhuri nahin hai (to kya hukm hai?), Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo khoon baha dey padhi. aur is par Allah ka naam yani Bismillah padha gaya ho to usey khaao , siwaaye daant aur nakhun sey zibeh kiye gaey janwer key , aur main tum sey daant aur nakhun ki padhi. tafseer bayan karta hun : daant , haddi hai aur nakhun habshiyon ki chhuri hai. Muhammad bin Bashaar ki sanad sey ye bayan kiya, Sufiyan Sory kehtey hain Abaaya bin Rifaa sey , aur Abaaya ney Raafey bin khadij sey aur Raafey ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi jaisi hadees riwayat ki, is mein (Abaaya an Abeeh) ka zikr nahin hai aur yehi baat ziyada sahih hai, Abaaya ney Raafey sey suna hai, ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, wo daant aur haddi sey zibeh karna durust nahin samajhtey hain."
1492,"Hum log Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath eik safar mein they, logon key oonton mein sey eik oont bidak kar bhag gaya, unkey paas ghodey bhi na they, eik aadmi ney us ko teer maara so Allah ney us ko rok diya, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''in chopayon mein jangli janweron ki tarah bhagodey bhi hotey hain, isliye agar un mein sey koi aisa karey (yani bidak jaey) to uskey sath isi tarah karo.'' is sanad sey bhi Raafey (Raziallahu anhu) sey usi jaisi hadees marvi (riwayat hui) hai, is mein ye nahin zikr hai ke Abaaya ney apney walid sey riwayat ki, ye ziyada sahih hai. 1- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. 2- isi tarah Shoba ney isey Saeed bin Masruq sey Sufiyan ki hadees ki tarah riwayat hai."
